| Governance > Policy & Compliance       | Cap. 2, Cap. 14                                           |
| Governance > Education & Guidance      | Cap. 13                                                   |
| Governance > Risk Management           | Cap. 1, Cap. 3, Cap. 5                                    |
| Design > Threat Assessment             | Cap. 3, Cap. 4                                            |
| Design > Security Requirements         | Cap. 2, Cap. 3                                            |
| Implementation > Secure Build          | Cap. 5, Cap. 7, Cap. 8, Cap. 9                            |
| Implementation > Secure Deployment     | Cap. 11, Cap. 7                                           |
| Verification > Architecture Assessment | Cap. 4, Cap. 3                                            |
| Verification > Requirements Driven Testing | Cap. 2, Cap. 10                                     |
| Verification > Security Testing        | Cap. 10                                                   |
| Operations > Incident Management       | Cap. 12, Cap. 1                                           |
| Operations > Environment Management    | Cap. 7, Cap. 11                                           |

